<L>__{exterior elevated train station dawn}
<A>__{heading along spring garden street, rocky passes beneath an elevated train station. the roaring train overhead seems to blend perfectly with his muscular running style.}
<L>__{exterior docks dawn}
<A>__{the sky is beginning to lighten. the fighter now runs along the piers and past anchored freighters.}
<L>__{exterior eastern packing company dawn}
<A>__{it is five thirty and rocky approaches the loading platform belonging to eastern packing company. alongside the loading platform come several boxcars. rocky mounts the ramp and knocks on the metal door. it soon opens and paulie guides him inside. paulie is drunk.}
